metadata.name: Mainframe Maiden
metadata.description:
The Mainframe Maiden is an android designed for infiltrating and sabotaging enemy computer systems. She is equipped with a powerful onboard computer and a wide range of hacking tools and techniques.  
 
Her artificial intelligence is expertly designed for deception and subterfuge, and she is capable of human-like emotions and expressions. Her metal body is sleek and agile, and she moves with the grace and stealth of a cat. 

She is the perfect technician for cyber-warfare, and she will stop at nothing to achieve her objectives.
